high_descs: Take a step to the left to face the white table.
Pick up the knife on the table.
TUrn right and walk forward to face the trash can.
Cut the apple in the trash can into three pieces.
Place the knife in the trash can.
Pick up a piece of apple from the trash can.
Turn around and step forward to face the microwave.
Heat the apple piece in the microwave and remove it.
Take a step to the right to face the fridge.
Place the apple piece in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the white table
Grab the knife off of the table
Turn right and go to the trash can
Slice the apple in the trash can
Put the knife in the trash can
Pick up a slice of the apple
Turn right and go to the microwave
Heat the sliced apple in the microwave and then take it out
Turn right and go to the fridge
Put the sliced apple in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Putting a hot apple slice in the fridge

high_descs: turn left, then go straight to the door, after which you should face the table on the right
pick up the knife on the white table
turn right, then go straight to the green waste bin
slice the apple in the waste bin
place the knife in the waste bin next to the apple slices
pick up a slice of apple in the waste bin
turn around, then move to the opposite side of the kitchen to face the microwave
place the apple slice in the microwave to the right of the egg, let it heat for several seconds, then open the door and take the slice out
face the refrigerator to the right of the microwave
open the refrigerator and place the apple slice on the middle shelf, then close the door
anns.task_desc: slice an apple in the waste bin and heat it up so it can go in the refrigerator for storage
